item_name: Giovanna Collection Women's 3-piece Lace and Silk Wool Skirt Suit
product_description: This sophisticated skirt suit offers a jacket, camisole and skirt. Crafted of quality polyester, this suit is designed to impress your colleagues for many meetings to come. Jacket is made with virtual silk with gathered satin trim on waistline, olivets clasp closure. Satin camisole with lace overlay in the front panel. Lace overlay straight skirt with side elastic and back zipper. Measurements taken from size 10: jacket length from center back = 26", camisole length = 23", skirt length = 32". Hats on model are NOT included.
